      Master Every Shot, One Cup at a Time
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
      Join thousands of coffee lovers who use Visualizer to track, analyze, and perfect their coffee. Whether you're pulling espresso or brewing filter coffee, we've got you covered.
